node.text: @KimKardashian is obsessed with the Cotton Jersey collection, and so are we! This fabric is the softest, stretchiest, most breathable cotton you’ll ever wear. From the most flattering tees to everyday underwear to bralettes with more support and hold than ever—you’ll reach for these styles everyday. Promise.
